**Naming Convention for Examples:**
- Main demo: `{component}-demo.tsx`
- Variants: `{component}-{variant}.tsx` (e.g., `button-destructive.tsx`, `button-outline.tsx`)
- Feature variations: `{component}-{feature}.tsx` (e.g., `button-with-icon.tsx`)
- Complex examples: `{component}-{use-case}.tsx` (e.g., `button-group-dropdown.tsx`)

